{
  "stem": "23410.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it is that somebody has to be responsible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, afterwards, 120 and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is also to divide the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had different groups in the death brigade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One group was the digging group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other group was carrying the corpses to the wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We laid out wood and burned when there were about 2,000 bodies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, you carried the dead body, and you laid it down, one-- one order of wood, and afterwards bodies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Afterwards, next wood, afterward, bodies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so-- and afterwards, when it was high enough at about 2,000 bodies, you put on kerosene over it, and you set it on fire.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the fire was finished--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took overnight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] A day and a night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes a little long, sometimes a little-- depending how dry it is, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the bodies have finished, there was another group that was called ash colony, colony of ashes, that took the ashes over to a place where it was only stone, and people sat down around it with sieves, and sieved out the ashes.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the gold or any valuables were taken out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if it wasn't something burned completely, it went back to be burned completely to ashes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See, that's why it was called ash colony.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, there were different groups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Normally, to the ash colony, were people a little bit weaker, older-- older, what I mean, 40 years or 35 years.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you were 20 years, you were in the digging group, and if you were 25 years old or 28, you were a carrier.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You carried the bodies to this wood thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
